  <brief_title>Randomized Controlled Trial on Uptake of NHS Health Checks</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial to Compare the Effect of Two New Behaviourally Enhanced NHS Health Check Leaflets and the Current Nationally Recommended Leaflet on Uptake of NHS Health Checks</official_title>
  <sponsors>
